<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> kOccaṭaiya paṉmarāṉa <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>cun=taracoḷa pā<hi rend="grantha">ṇḍhyade</hi>vaṟku <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>Āka ney Uḻakkum Irāmaṇaraṅkaṉ ceramāṉār Irāciṅkatevar paṇṭāra <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>ṉār Irāciṅkatevar paṇṭārattu pacu Irupattaiñcu koṇṭu kaṭava ney Uḻakkum Iv <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>peṟṟāṉ paṭāraṉ ceramāṉār Irāciṅkatevar paṇṭārattu Erumai mūṉṟu koṇṭu kaṭava ne <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>Āḻākkkum Ivvūr paṭākai vaḻutiyūr Irukkum veḷḷāḷaṉ māl cūṟṟi vaicca Erumai mu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>ku kaṭava ney Āḻākkey Iruceviṭarai caṭaiyaṉ cūṟṟi ceramāṉār koṇṭu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>ṭārattu Erumai Iraṇṭum pacu nāluṅ koṇṭu kaṭava ney <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>Aṭṭakkaṭava ney Āḻākku Ivaṉukkup puṇaimalaikuruntaṉ ma <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/>mūṉṟu koṇṭu kaṭava ney Āḻākkum Accalam pāṇṭaṉ I <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
</p>

